aboutDescription: Hello! My name is Athul and I am a budding Software Engineer from A J INSTITUTE OF ENGINEERING AND TECHNOLOGY in Visvesvaraya Technological University. I will be graduating with my Bachelor's degree in Computer Science Engineering in Augest of 2021. I interned as a Software Engineer at Suven Consultants & Technology Pvt. Ltd, and I cannot wait for my next journey. I'm most passionate about giving back to the community, and my goal is to pursue this passion within the field of software engineering!
